Dan Gillmor was a influential technology reporter and columnus for Silicon Valley newspapers and outlets such as the San Jose Mercury News and SiliconValley.com and became an advocate for promoting citizen-based journalism efforts, which he describes and explains in the book We The Media.

His main blog is at [http://bayosphere.com/blog/dangillmor] 

We The Media, book and weblog about citizen journalism, at [http://wethemedia.oreilly.com/]

